1505:CMSIS/core_cm4.h **** /** \brief  Set Priority Grouping
1506:CMSIS/core_cm4.h **** 
1507:CMSIS/core_cm4.h ****   The function sets the priority grouping field using the required unlock sequence.
1508:CMSIS/core_cm4.h ****   The parameter PriorityGroup is assigned to the field SCB->AIRCR [10:8] PRIGROUP field.
1509:CMSIS/core_cm4.h ****   Only values from 0..7 are used.
